  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT295-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">vāyil vēṇṭic ceṉṟa kiḻavaṟkut tōḻi uraittatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Told by the confidante to HIM who went wishing for the
          door/mediation. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT295">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> uṭuttun toṭuttum pūṇṭuñ cerīiyun</l>
          <l> taḻaiyaṇip polinta vāyamoṭu tuvaṉṟi</l>
          <l> viḻavoṭu varuti nīyē yiḵtō</l>
          <l> vōrāṉ valcic cīril vāḻkkai</l>
          <l> perunalak kuṟumakaḷ vanteṉa</l>
          <l> viṉiviḻa vāyiṟ ṟeṉṉumiv vūrē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l rend="indent4">Wrapping up and tying and applying and inserting −</l>
          <l>you may come to the festival,</l>
          <l rend="indent">full with [her] companions dazzling with foliage [and] ornaments.</l>
          <l>This? This village says now it has become a festival ,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">because the little woman of great beauty has come,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">with a livelihood not enough for the food of one cow. </l>

          <lg type="alternate" sameAs="3+4b" resp="#Srin">
            <l> ... This?</l>
            <l>Food [is what is given by] one cow. Living without honour.</l>
          </lg>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
